{"tid":1764774,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【尋人】保良局李城璧中學/香港專業教育學院既麻煩入一入黎！","createTime":"2019-12-01T10:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T16:27:37.000Z","uid":79010,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fe2532198d83a98364f1f57a0c857394b7e8bfc2","tid":1764774,"uid":79010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T10:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f8pBrFm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff8pBrFm.jpg&h=c26ff59d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此人工黎日本工作假期後竟然向在日港人借錢後就唔還兼走佬！<br />\n<br />\n本來係因為大家同為香港人，又係外地獨自打拼，所以好心幫一幫佢，但無諗到對方竟然一拖再拖，而家仲打算一走了之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經試過用好多方法搵佢，可惜而家佢tg長期單剔，ig亦被佢unfriend，電話又唔接，去佢屋企又無人／唔應門，連去佢公司都話佢無返工！係無辦法之下，唯有嘗試網上尋人，而家已經對佢完全失望，所以希望搵到佢既屋企人，由佢屋企人代為勸佢還錢又好，又或者佢屋企人代為還錢都得，金額總共係19萬日元。希望大家可以盡量幫我share出去，比多啲人見到佢既惡行，亦希望盡快聯絡到佢家人。<br />\n<br />\n若有認識他/他家人的校友，希望可以做做好心，提供資料給受害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c873b4c759cb607a981d09407ef323abb7434f15","tid":1764774,"uid":79010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T11:14:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae45a46ccb3315ef7fbe3d61a4fce8614bccacbb","tid":1764774,"uid":109654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T11:23:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1b8505b909f4494fb9a8cbabbd9828e742f93f5","tid":1764774,"uid":34209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T11:28:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad2a530b3fa073658b67061512f06ae9f7fec864","tid":1764774,"uid":235497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T11:30:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1228f8a4b43d375f1099f8b63e139f3bb957fb0f","tid":1764774,"uid":24744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T11:56:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"754751157a5940ca6d4f66235bddd04c5ed555b6","tid":1764